{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2638928, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 503682, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "对于社会整体来说，医学能防治新冠这种大规模传染病就够了，疑难杂症癌症这种您就抓紧享福听天由命吧。攻克一种全人类不到一百例的疑难杂症所需投入的资源或许可以极大的改善数万人的生活。", "timestamp": 1633105727, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2638959, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 503682, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "医学发展得很不完善大多还停留在经验上", "timestamp": 1633105984, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2638994, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 503682, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "30年医学不会那么厉害，不过估计有可能可以把你的脑子克隆到电脑上，你就永生了。", "timestamp": 1633106291, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2639032, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 503682, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "癌症现在生存率提高的很多啊", "timestamp": 1633106641, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2639786, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 503682, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "很多病是人均寿命提高之后才开始出现了。新冠在古代那个年龄结构下完全造成不了这么大的影响。", "timestamp": 1633121781, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 503682, "reply": 5, "tag": null, "text": "30年后医学会发展到什么程度？\n感觉现在好多疑难杂症 癌症 都没办法治好啊", "timestamp": 1633104517, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1633121783, "url": "", "vote": {}}}